    public class POPOPrivKey
extends java.lang.Object

    CRMF POPOPrivKey: 
     POPOPrivKey ::= CHOICE {
      thisMessage         [0] BIT STRING,
      subsequentMessage   [1] SubsequentMessage,
      dhMAC               [2] BIT STRING }

 SubsequentMessage ::= INTEGER {
      encrCert        (0),
      challengeResp   (1) }
